<?xml version="1.0" encoding="utf-8"?>
<Subtitle>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>1</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>11193</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>16067</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>新年后的一个星期一。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>2</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>16068</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>20830</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>科学课上，乔伊正在听贝柔老师讲天气。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>3</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>20831</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>23293</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>她递给凯蒂一张纸条，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>4</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>23294</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>27377</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>上面写道：要是雨停了就好了！</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>5</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>27378</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>30388</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>凯蒂点头，叹了口气。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>6</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>30389</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>33763</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>柳树溪这几天一直在下雨。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>7</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>33764</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>36397</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>乔伊希望下的是雪！</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>8</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>36398</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>40630</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“请把科学书收起来。” 贝柔老师说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>9</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>40631</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>43375</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>该上社会研究课了。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>10</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>43376</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>47577</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“谁知道一月份有什么节日？”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>11</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>47578</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>49860</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>劳拉举起了手。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>12</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>49861</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>53373</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“有 ‘马丁∙路德∙金纪念日’。” 她说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>13</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>53374</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>59713</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“对！谁知道马丁∙路德∙金做了什么？” 贝柔老师问。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>14</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>59714</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>64221</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“他提倡种族平等。” 卡洛斯回答说，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>15</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>64222</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>67289</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text> “黑人和白人可以去同样的学校，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>16</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>67290</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>69789</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>也可以住在同一个小区。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>17</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>69790</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>73875</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“是的。为了自由，他做了演讲，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>18</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>73876</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>77451</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>还领导了游行。” 贝柔老师说，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>19</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>77452</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>81262</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“他为了自己的信仰而奋斗！</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>20</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>81263</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>86563</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>他也因此成为了美国历史上伟大的领袖之一。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>21</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>86564</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>90857</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>贝柔老师在白板上写下了 “领袖” 二字。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>22</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>90858</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>96765</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我们的下一个社会研究发表是关于美国领袖的。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>23</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>96766</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>100048</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>她给每个人发了一张作业纸，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>24</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>100049</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>103658</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>上面写着：“是什么造就了领袖？”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>25</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>103659</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>106999</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“大家选择一个著名的历史人物，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>26</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>107000</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>112137</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>说一说是什么让这个人成为了一个伟大的领袖。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>27</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>112138</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>116222</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>之后，希望你们能在接下来的一周里，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>28</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>116223</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>118907</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>像这个领袖一样生活。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>29</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>118908</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>123702</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“这个发表一定会很有意思的。” 乔伊想。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>30</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>123703</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>127278</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我觉得选乔治·华盛顿不错。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>31</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>127279</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>132502</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>那我得戴一顶有三只角的可笑帽子吗？” 凯蒂问。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>32</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>132503</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>134318</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>贝柔老师笑了。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>33</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>134319</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>136637</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“不是的，凯蒂。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>34</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>136638</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>139314</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>是希望你偶尔可以想一下，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>35</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>139315</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>143919</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>‘如果是乔治·华盛顿，他会怎么做’ 的意思。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>36</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>143920</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>149054</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我想写关于乔治·华盛顿的发表。” 卡洛斯说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>37</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>149055</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>153561</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“是我先想到他的。” 凯蒂翻了个白眼，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>38</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>153562</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>158044</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“不过，好吧！我选亚伯拉罕·林肯好了。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>39</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>158045</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>162797</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我要选马丁·路德·金。” 卢克大声说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>40</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>162798</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>168174</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>同学们开始大声地喊出许多著名领袖的名字。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>41</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>168175</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>172255</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>乔伊安静地坐在她的座位上思考着，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>42</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>172256</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>176887</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>她想为自己的发表选一个完美的领袖。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>43</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>176888</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>183162</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>双胞胎姐妹俩放学回到家时，爷爷正在厨房里。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>44</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>183163</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>187212</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>他正从烤箱里拿出一盘巧克力饼干。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>45</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>187213</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>190849</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“你们回来得正好。” 他说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>46</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>190850</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>197527</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“好香啊！谢谢爷爷。” 凯蒂边说边坐在了桌旁。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>47</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>197528</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>200360</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>乔伊走向冰箱。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>48</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>200361</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>203978</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>她给自己和凯蒂各倒了一杯牛奶。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>49</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>203979</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>208898</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“爷爷，您最喜欢的美国领袖是谁？” 乔伊问。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>50</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>208899</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>214803</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“嗯，应该是富兰克林·德拉诺·罗斯福总统。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>51</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>214804</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>218098</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>他帮我们国家走出了大萧条。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>52</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>218099</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>219991</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>人们失去了一切。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>53</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>219992</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>223856</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>如：工作、房子、甚至金钱。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>54</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>223857</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>227896</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>罗斯福总统找到办法帮了很多人。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>55</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>227897</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>230730</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>爷爷回答，“怎么了？”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>56</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>230731</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>234728</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我们学校在准备一个关于领袖的发表。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>57</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>234729</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>237722</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>凯蒂边吃着饼干边说道，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>58</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>237723</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>240702</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我选了亚伯拉罕·林肯。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>59</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>240703</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>243676</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>尽管会被很多人憎恶，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>60</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>243677</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>246663</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>他还是勇敢的说他不喜欢奴隶制。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>61</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>246664</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>253914</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“还有，他在美国内战时，也非常努力地工作。” 爷爷补充说，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>62</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>253915</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>258995</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“对于你的发表来说，林肯是一个很棒的选择。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>63</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>258996</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>261800</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>乔伊皱起了眉头。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>64</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>261801</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>265310</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>她还是不知道该选哪个领袖。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>65</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>265311</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>269562</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“哦！已经四点半了！”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>66</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>269563</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>273645</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>她抬头看了一眼墙上的钟表，说道，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>67</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>273646</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>277690</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我得去喂鸡，写作业，练小提琴了！”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>68</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>277691</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>282593</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“还有，一会儿你得洗碗。” 爷爷提醒她，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>69</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>282594</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>286862</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“因为晚饭后，我和你爸爸要去钓鱼。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>70</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>286863</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>289122</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>乔伊已经忘了，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>71</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>289123</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>293096</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>每年的这个时候，爷爷和爸爸都要去钓鱼。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>72</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>293097</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>298200</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>这意味着她和凯蒂这个星期会有更多的家务活。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>73</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>298201</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>300845</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>她从椅子上跳了起来。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>74</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>300846</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>305315</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>这个星期会很忙！</Text>
  </Paragraph>
</Subtitle>